This torrent works perfectly.  Be sure to click the Copy button in the activation dialog otherwise the code doesn't work.

The keygen does work, but the directions skip some steps.  The directions should be:

1. Install GoodSync, obviously...

2. Register with the use of the keygen. Chose online activation via browser.
   a. Enter your username and think of a 10 digit OrderID. 
   b. Click NEXT
   c. Click the COPY button
   d. Paste this into the keygen's "Request Code" box
   e. Generate the code (click "gimme"), copy it, and paste it into the Activation Code box in Goodsync

3. Enjoy! ;)
